\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line Regent Business School is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a private higher education provider and is accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC.  The institution is currently offering a Bachelor of Commerce at Level 6 with 360 credits. The institution has also applied for a Bachelor of Commerce at level 7. \cell \pard 

